version 2 

Do this based on a story in a file.  To represent blanks,
put a dollar sign and then type of word to be replaced.
If you want to re-use what was in a previous blank, mark
that by a percent sign and then a number (index of the blank,
starting at 0 of course).

eg.
When I was in $ place, I bought a pet $ animal.
I traded $ number $ thing to get the % 1


